suggestions.txt: Why did the chicken cross the road?

I work at a grocery store, bagging people's stuff. An old lady came through the checkout lane, and I asked her whether she'd like paper or plastic. She replied 'You can put it in either one, but make sure you don't squish my buns.'
Why did the chicken cross the road?

curSuggs.txt: I was watching the TV show Border Wars which is about the U.S. Border Patrol. They found drugs in the back of a vehicle and one of the agents said, 'There's a huge load in the rear.'
